INSERT INTO color_schemes (slug, name, primaryColor, secondaryColor, accentColor, accentDarkColor, backgroundColor, secondaryLightColor, description, sortOrder, isActive) VALUES 
('valentine-gift', 'Valentine''s Day', '#c41e3a', '#8b1a2d', '#fff5f5', '#ffe8e8', '#fff8f8', '#fce8eb', 'Romantic red and pink color scheme for Valentine''s Day event', 1, 1),
('mothers-day', 'Mother''s Day', '#9b6b6b', '#7a5454', '#fff9f9', '#f5e6e6', '#fffafa', '#f5eaea', 'Soft mauve color scheme for Mother''s Day event', 2, 1),
('fathers-day', 'Father''s Day', '#2c5282', '#1a365d', '#f0f5ff', '#e2e8f0', '#f8fafc', '#e8eef8', 'Deep navy blue color scheme for Father''s Day event', 3, 1),
('black-friday', 'Black Friday', '#000000', '#1a1a1a', '#fff9f0', '#ffe8cc', '#fffbf5', '#fff3e0', 'Black and gold color scheme for Black Friday event', 4, 1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name=VALUES(name);
